divs: Sighting Details I JUST WANT TO KNOW IF ANY OTHERS HAVE SEEN OBJECTS AROUND THE SALTON SEA IN CALIFORNIA? I SAW THEM TWO YEARS IN A ROW AND EVEN HAD A WITNESS AT THE SECOND EVENT. MOST OF THE ELDERLY RESIDENTS SEEMED NOT TO WANT TO DISCUSS THEM.... WIERD. THERE WERE MANY!! THEY WERE VERY SLOW MOVING AND WOULDNT ATTRACT ATTENTION FROM MOST DRIVERS. THIS IS A VERY REMOTE LOCATION AND EDWARDS AF BASE SENT JETS FOLLOWING MY CALL TO THEM.
